summary: AN ORDINANCE providing for the acquisition by condemnation of land and other property in and adjoining Blocks 448, 448-A, 449, 449-A, 452 and 453, Seattle Tide Lands, Extension \#1, as established and platted pursuant to Law in 1927; together with that portion of Southwest Georgia Street vacated by Ordinance 66342 and that portion of Southwest Maryland Place vacated by Ordinance 97125, for an addition to the Don Armeni Boat Launching Ramp, Park and Recreation Facility.
